title: Dragons' Den-backed Lost My Name launches new space book
text: Retail and Consumer Dragons' Den-backed Lost My Name launches new space book Kids book, The Incredible Intergalactic Journey Home, has sold 1,000 copies pre-launch as parents rush to snap up the new hi-tech personalised product Dragon Piers Linney (centre) with the Lost My Name founders and characters from the flagship book By Rebecca Burn-Callander , Enterprise Editor 6:49PM BST 21 Sep 2015
